These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, almond-milk, lemonade
City: london, colone, rome, paris
4 different pets are kept: cat, rat, lizard, hamster
1. the owner of the cat is the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
5. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
6. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the owner of the rat is on the far left or far right##3
8. the owner of the hamster is between the person traveling to paris and the person drinking 7up##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage         | lemonade      | 7up | mirinda | almond-milk |
| City   | rome | london  | colone   | paris    |
| Pet     | cat     | lizard    | hamster    | rat      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, basketball, sailing, handball
4 different pets are kept: mouse, frog, fish, pony
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk, juice, iced-tea
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
2. the person who's sport is handball is the owner of the fish##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is in an even position##4
4. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
7. the owner of the mouse is between the person who's sport is handball and the person who's sport is basketball##2
8. the owner of the pony is between the owner of the frog and the person who's sport is sailing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport         | handball | sailing   | basketball | swimming  |
| Pet   | fish     | mouse | pony  | frog |
| Beverage     | iced-tea        | juice  | almond-milk    | coffee |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, lily, daffodil, iris
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, chess, dancing, fishing
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, soy-milk, sprite
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who growsaconite and the person who growsiris##2
2. the person who's hobby is chess is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person drinking cola is the person who growsdaffodil##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
5. the person who growsiris is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who growslily and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Flower          | aconite | lily   | iris     | daffodil     |
| Hobby   | chess  | fishing | dancing   | card-games  |
| Beverage     | sprite      | mirinda | soy-milk | cola |

