.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, azalea, rose, daffodil
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, blend, montecristo, fonseca
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, sprite, coffee, 7up
1. the fonseca-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the person who growsazalea is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
5. the fonseca-smoker is the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person who growsrose is the old-henry-smoker##1
7. the montecristo-smoker is the person who growssunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Flower   | sunflower  | daffodil   | rose     | azalea |
| Cigar   | montecristo  | fonseca      | old-henry        | blend     |
| Beverage         | coffee | lemonade | 7up | sprite   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, snake, mouse, goat
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, freelancer, dancer, manager
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, august, march, november
1. the owner of the goat is the manager##1
2. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in may is the manager##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the manager##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is in an even position##4
6. the freelancer is on the far left##1
7. the owner of the snake is on the far right##1
8. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
9. the software-developer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Pet   | lizard   | goat   | mouse | snake |
| Job         | freelancer      | manager | software-developer      | dancer |
| Birthday     | august | may        | november       | march  |

