.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, almond-milk, fanta, tea
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, march, november, january
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, tulip, zinnia, daisy
1. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage    | fanta   | tea      | almond-milk       | iced-tea |
| Birthday   | august | january | november     | march |
| Flower     | daisy     | tulip  | dahlia | zinnia |

