.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, dubstep, house, electronic
City: colone, miami, hamburg, prague
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, june, march, april
1. the person who's birthday is in march is the person traveling to colone##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person traveling to prague and the person who's birthday is in september##2
3. the person traveling to prague is the fan of dubstep##1
4. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
5. the fan of indie is in an even position##4
6. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
7. the person traveling to colone is the fan of indie##1
8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Music-Genre      | house   | electronic          | dubstep | indie        |
| City   | hamburg     | miami | prague   | colone     |
| Birthday           | september | june         | april         | march |

