.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
City: london, paris, berlin, boston
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, almond-milk, fanta, sprite
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, frog, mouse, goldfish
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
2. the person drinking fanta is the person traveling to london##1
3. the person drinking sprite is the person traveling to berlin##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
5. the owner of the frog is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person traveling to london##2
6. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
7. the person traveling to london is in an even position##4
8. the person traveling to london is between the person traveling to paris and the person traveling to berlin##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| City         | paris | london      | berlin       | boston    |
| Beverage           | almond-milk  | fanta  | sprite | iced-tea |
| Pet   | goldfish      | mouse | frog         | guinea-pig    |

