.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, taxi, quad-bike, boat
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, august, november, september
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, family, animation, comedy
1. the person who's birthday is in february is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
3. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
4. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person driving the car##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person driving the car##1
8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
9. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Transport   | taxi         | car  | quad-bike     | boat         |
| Birthday        | september | august | february | november         |
| Movie-Genre      | family         | animation  | epic   | comedy |

