.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, august, october, july
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, bellflower, daisy, poppy
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, 7up, sprite
 1. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
 2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 4. the person who growsdaisy is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in june##2
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
 6. the person drinking sprite is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 7. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who growsbellflower is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in october##2
10. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Birthday   | june  | october    | august | july    |
| Flower   | daffodil | daisy | bellflower  | poppy |
| Beverage           | 7up   | sprite    | hot-chocolate        | tea   |

