.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, golf, volleyball, ice-hockey
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, kiwi, garlic, broccoli
4 different pets are kept: hamster, frog, horse, hedgehog
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person eating garlic##3
4. the person eating kiwi is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
8. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
9. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Sport      | surfing                | ice-hockey  | golf | volleyball   |
| Food           | broccoli | kiwi | cucumber   | garlic |
| Pet   | frog         | hamster     | hedgehog     | horse |

