.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, cola, mirinda, almond-milk
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, aristoff, siglo, prince
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, traveling, hiking, chess
1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the prince-smoker and the person who's hobby is chess##2
6. the siglo-smoker is in an even position##4
7. the person drinking water is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage          | mirinda    | cola  | almond-milk  | water |
| Cigar   | prince | aristoff | old-henry | siglo |
| Hobby   | hiking    | drawing     | chess    | traveling |

