.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
House: modern, wooden, townhouse, ranch-style
4 different games are played: domino, backgammon, poker, chess
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, boat, jet-ski, bike
1. the person driving the boat is between the townhouse house and the person playing domino##2
2. the modern house is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
4. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the person driving the bike is in an odd position##4
6. the wooden house is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
7. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
8. the person playing poker is the modern house##1
9. the person playing chess is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the trike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| House      | modern | townhouse      | wooden  | ranch-style    |
| Game   | poker   | backgammon | chess | domino |
| Transport           | bike      | jet-ski       | boat   | trike      |

