.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, peas, garlic, banana
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, house, blues, funk
4 different pets are kept: cat, frog, snake, turtle
1. the person eating garlic is in an even position##4
2. the person eating peas is between the person eating banana and the owner of the cat##2
3. the owner of the frog is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating banana is in an even position##4
5. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
6. the fan of funk is between the owner of the cat and the fan of disco##2
7. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
8. the fan of house is in an even position##4
9. the owner of the cat is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Food         | apricot    | garlic | peas  | banana  |
| Music-Genre   | blues | house       | funk | disco |
| Pet         | snake   | cat      | turtle | frog       |

