.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
4 different games are played: bridge, whist, chess, billiard
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi, car, boat
There are 4 different nationalities: british, german, japanese, thai
1. the german is in an even position##4
2. the german is the person playing whist##1
3. the person playing whist is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person playing chess is the person driving the boat##1
5. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is the german##1
7. the british is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
8. the thai is the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Game      | chess      | whist | bridge     | billiard    |
| Transport   | boat | quad-bike      | taxi | car |
| Nationality           | japanese   | german  | british     | thai |

