1. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
2. the person playing bridge is in an even position##4
3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far left##1
4. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
5. the person traveling to colone is between the person who growsaconite and the person playing billiard##2
6. the person who growstulip is the person playing poker##1
7. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
8. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| City    | prague    | colone     | san-francisco    | boston        |
| Game       | billiard   | bridge | monopoly | poker |
| Flower   | daffodil | sunflower      | aconite    | tulip   |

