4. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who growsaconite##1
5. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
6. the person who growsdaffodil is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
8. the person who likes azure is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |        4        |
