.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-19::.
4 different games are played: chess, bridge, poker, whist
House: townhouse, gothic-revival, ranch-style, wooden
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, carrot, lemon, raspberry
1. the person eating raspberry is in an even position##4
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
3. the gothic-revival house is on the far left##1
4. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the wooden house##1
5. the person playing chess is the person eating grapefruit##1
6. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
7. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person playing whist##1
8. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Game   | whist | bridge | chess | poker   |
| House   | gothic-revival    | wooden   | ranch-style     | townhouse    |
| Food   | carrot  | lemon | grapefruit  | raspberry |

