.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, writer, journalist, analyst
House: gothic-revival, farmhouse, townhouse, art-deco
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, family, animation, western
1. the engineer is in an odd position##4
2. the art-deco house is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
4. the journalist is on the far left##1
5. the writer is between the art-deco house and the gothic-revival house##2
6. the farmhouse house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
7. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the engineer##1
8. the person watching family movies is on the left of the writer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Job    | journalist    | writer    | engineer  | analyst |
| House   | art-deco | farmhouse | gothic-revival | townhouse      |
| Movie-Genre     | family   | crime        | western   | animation       |

 